data.description: SEE PROPERTY VIDEO TOUR!!! Check out this rare and unique contemporary California rancher!  This 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home features NEW VINYL PLANK FLOORING throughout.  Upon entering the front door, you'll be greeted by the open living room area with an adjacent oversize dining room area accompanied by an ample sized kitchen.  The kitchen features black matching appliances which include a built-in microwave, wall oven, dishwasher and refrigerator with ice maker.  The washer and dryer are also found here as well as a pass-through area to the dining room.  Heading down the hallway, you'll find a full bath as well as 2 adequate size bedrooms.  Opposite of those is the primary bedroom with a sliding door leading to the en-suite full bath.  Enjoy evenings on the semi-private porch/carport area as well as a fully fenced back yard.  Did you say storage?  Check out the large storage room at the rear of the carport area as well as the shed in the back yard.  Combine all of this with a great neighborhood location, central air, vinyl windows, maintenance free stucco exterior and unique low slope roof and you may have just found the property for which you've been looking!  100% conventional financing IS available for this property - contact listing agent for details.  2 hour notice for showings please. Note, owner may be present for showings and settlement is subject to owner finding suitable housing.
